    "ideation": "The nut and bolt emoji should feel like industrial precision, torque, and structural integrity. Instead of a soft organic face, Logos performs as a mechanical assembly. The eyes represent the hex-head of the bolt, starting out slightly misaligned and loose. The mouth is the thread: a jagged, high-frequency wave. The animation arc simulates the process of being tightened: a series of jerky, rotational movements (torque steps) where the eyes and lids 'grip' harder. At the peak, the frequency of the mouth wave increases to represent the intense metal-on-metal friction and tension of a final quarter-turn. It ends with a solid, unshakeable lock, vibrating slightly with stored kinetic energy. Colors are cold, industrial steels and galvanized blues.",
